        <section class="mt-4">
            <h2>Trading vs Investing</h2>
            <p>
                While often used interchangeably, trading and investing are distinct. Trading typically involves shorter-term 
                transactions aimed at profiting from market fluctuations. 
                Investing, on the other hand, is about building wealth over a longer period through the buying and holding of assets.
            </p>
