            <h2>Risks and Rewards</h2>
            <p>
                Trading offers the potential for significant profits but also comes with high risks. Market volatility can lead 
                to substantial losses, making it crucial for traders to be well-educated and to use risk management strategies.
            </p>
          
            <p>
               Formula to calculate Risk-Reward ratio: Risk – Reward Ratio = Potential Risk in Trading / Expected Rewards
